release_note: Fixed compatibility issues with some new devices.
Change the interface to be compatible with iOS 7 and on iPhone 5
Fix some errors that cause app crashes

Added My Music feature. With the My Music feature you will create your own karaoke songs that Soncamedia has not yet updated. The songs in the My Music section also have all the same features as any song in the Music Store : Sing now view lyrics add to the song you are singing record ... Edit settings interface Fix some errors compatible with OS version 6.1
Add scoring feature after each end of the song Fix error of not being able to record songs on iPhone Improve song update speed when installing the application
